name: souls
description:
the album cover to my beattape "souls" that released on August 27, 2021. the project is a culmination of three years worth of learning how to make music, discovering my style and creating something I am proud of. 

on top of creating the music, I used an AI to help generate the art for the project. 1 for each track, also available on HEN. 

if you but this piece or any other piece from "souls" I will send you the high quality AIFF files! 

Appreciate the support greatly! "souls" is also available on all major streaming platforms, link is in my twitter bio. @ryanartwalker
